     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <pb facs="34"/>
   <head>❧To the Reader.</head>
   <l>WHat age in Infantes is requirde,</l>
   <l>or ere they should bée taught,</l>
   <l>What sort of Teachers best agrées,</l>
   <l>what Schooles bée good, what naught,</l>
   <l>Dewe meanes also t'instruct them well,</l>
   <l>all these good Readers here</l>
   <l>Within this booke (though smal to vewe)</l>
   <l>in largest wise appeare.</l>
   <l>With other matters incident,</l>
   <l>which to my simple skill,</l>
   <l>For thy delite, I haue discourste</l>
   <l>and written with good will.</l>
   <l>My meaning doe accept for good:</l>
   <l>but pardon thinges amisse.</l>
   <l>So shall my penne for thy behoofe</l>
   <l>write greater thinges then this.</l>
</div>
